      "position": [
        -1632,
        192
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 560,
        "height": 736,
        "content": "## Policy Interpretation Agent\n**What** –OpenAI agent parses regulatory language and extracts structured policy signals.\n**Why** – Converts dense legal text into machine-readable insights that governance agents can act on."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "392f6ef8-5eea-48f0-bb95-f9bca7bbe139",
